Yandex KIT 5
Raid scripting exercise.

Written Sat Sep 27 2014 by the paw of the.l.a.cat.
You may reach me out at the.l.a.cat@gmail.com or the-l-a-cat at github.

Example usage:
# sh raid_manage.up.sh
# mdadm --manage /dev/md/ya_raid_0 --set-faulty /dev/loop1
# sh raid_manage.heal.sh
# sh raid_manage.down.sh

